Class SuggestionGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.smayfiel.autocorrectBacon.SuggestionGenerator

  • public class SuggestionGenerator
extends Object
    SuggestionGenerator gets suggestions from the three methods and returns them individually. One Suggestion Generator could be used multiple times, by calling different search methods.
